Claim your unique NFT for being part of our celebration.

How to get your NFT

Step 1. Get an Ethereum wallet app

If you have an iPhone or Android phone, we recommend using Rainbow Wallet. It's free from the App Store.

Step 2. Get an Ethereum wallet on Rainbow.

  1. Tap on "Get a new wallet".
  2. We recommend backing up your wallet to make sure you don't lose access!

Step 3. Tap on "Copy address".

Step 4. Open your unique NFT link and paste your address.

Hint: it's the big QR code we sent you 🙂

Step 5. Tap on "Mint POAP Token".

You can get it for free if you check the box for "Free minting in xDAI".

That's it!

If everything goes well, your shiny new NFT will be added to your address, ready for you to share with the world.

How to view your NFT

Step 1. Go to https://app.poap.xyz/.

Step 2. Tap on "input an address manually".

Step 3. Open Rainbow Wallet and tap on "Copy address".

Step 4. Paste your address into POAP and tap "Explore my collection".

That's it!
